{{Use Indian English|date=April 2018}}
The '''Cricket Academy of Pathans''' is a cricket academy in [[Vadodara]], [[Gujarat]]. The academy was jointly launched by [[Irfan Pathan]] and [[Yusuf Pathan]].Also CAP is part of 12 Cities like New Delhi,Noida,Patna,Surat etc.The academy has tied up with former India coach [[Greg Chappell]] and [[Cameron Tradell]] as chief mentors. It is considered as a failed operation by many cricket critics. Chappell would coach the coaches of the Academy.<ref>[http://indianexpress.com/article/sports/cricket/pathan-brothers-launch-cricket-academy-of-pathans/ Pathan brothers launch Cricket Academy of Pathans]</ref><ref>[http://www.rediff.com/cricket/report/pathan-brothers-yusuf-irfan-launch-cricket-academy-sign-up-greg-chappell/20140911.htm Pathan brothers launch cricket academy; sign up Greg Chappell]</ref><ref>[http://www.deccanchronicle.com/140912/sports-cricket/article/irfan-pathan-ropes-chappell-pathans-cricket-academy Irfan Pathan ropes in Chappell for Pathans Cricket Academy]</ref>

