'''Liga Deportiva del Amambay''' initialed '''LDA'''<ref>http://www.curuguatynews.com/deporte/general/la-liga-deportiva-del-amambay-cumple-60-anos-de-vida-institucional/15028</ref> is the department governing body for [[association football]] in the [[Amambay Department]] in [[Paraguay]]. It is affiliated with the [[Asociación Paraguaya de Fútbol]], the sport's national governing body.
The LDA was founded on 25 May 1953 during which only four clubs existed: [[Club Sportivo 2 de Mayo|Sportivo 2 de Mayo]], [[Club Aquidabán|Aquidabán]], [[Independiente Fútbol Club]] and [[Sportivo Obrero]].<ref>http://www.curuguatynews.com/deporte/general/la-liga-deportiva-del-amambay-cumple-60-anos-de-vida-institucional/15028</ref>
Liga Deportiva del Amambay's league is the [[Paraguayan Cuarta Division]] in the [[Paraguayan football league system]], where which the top clubs qualify for the [[Primera División B Nacional]], Paraguay's third division.
==Clubs== * [[América Foot Ball Club]]<ref>http://www.curuguatynews.com/deporte/general/la-liga-deportiva-del-amambay-cumple-60-anos-de-vida-institucional/15028</ref> * [[Club Aquidabán]]<ref>http://www.curuguatynews.com/deporte/general/la-liga-deportiva-del-amambay-cumple-60-anos-de-vida-institucional/15028</ref> * [[Club Atlético Bernardino Caballero]]<ref>http://www.curuguatynews.com/deporte/general/la-liga-deportiva-del-amambay-cumple-60-anos-de-vida-institucional/15028</ref> * [[Atlético Pedro Juan Caballero]]<ref>http://www.curuguatynews.com/deporte/general/la-liga-deportiva-del-amambay-cumple-60-anos-de-vida-institucional/15028</ref> * [[Club Deportivo 1º de Marzo]]<ref>http://www.curuguatynews.com/deporte/general/la-liga-deportiva-del-amambay-cumple-60-anos-de-vida-institucional/15028</ref> * [[General Diaz Foot Ball Club]]<ref>http://www.curuguatynews.com/deporte/general/la-liga-deportiva-del-amambay-cumple-60-anos-de-vida-institucional/15028</ref> * [[Club Sportivo 2 de Mayo]]<ref>http://www.curuguatynews.com/deporte/general/la-liga-deportiva-del-amambay-cumple-60-anos-de-vida-institucional/15028</ref> * [[Club Sportivo Obrero]]<ref>http://www.curuguatynews.com/deporte/general/la-liga-deportiva-del-amambay-cumple-60-anos-de-vida-institucional/15028</ref> * [[Independiente Fútbol Club]]<ref>http://www.curuguatynews.com/deporte/general/la-liga-deportiva-del-amambay-cumple-60-anos-de-vida-institucional/15028</ref> * [[Mariscal Estigarribia Fútbol Club]]<ref>http://www.curuguatynews.com/deporte/general/la-liga-deportiva-del-amambay-cumple-60-anos-de-vida-institucional/15028</ref>
