'''Peräseinäjoen Toive''' (PeTo) is a [[Finland|Finnish]] sports club from [[Seinäjoki]]. It has activity in [[Athletics (sport)|athletics]], [[floorball]], [[pesäpallo]], [[volleyball]], and [[wrestling]]. Peräseinäjoen Toive was founded in 1927 in [[Peräseinäjoki]].

